---

## Workflow

```
SUBMITTED
   ↓ Admin submits assessment (existing flow)
   ↓ Admin creates quotation → picks materials w/ MaterialPicker
PENDING_SA_APPROVAL
   ↓ SA reviews material table → adds remarks → approves
QUOTATION_SENT
   ↓ User sees "Action Required" banner in RequestDetailsModal → clicks Approve
   ↓ Inventory check runs: FROM_STOCK items deducted, rest → PENDING_PURCHASE
APPROVED
   ↓ Admin/SA triggers "Generate Vendor List"
VENDOR_LIST_PREPARED
   → VendorListsPage shows aggregated purchase list grouped by vendor
```

---

## Seed Data (loaded by DataInitializer on first boot)

- **10 materials**: Ply, Sunmica, Fevicol, Iron Nails, Labor Charges, Paint, Screws, Sandpaper, Wood Polish, Hinges
- **14 specifications**: 6mm/8mm/9mm/12mm Ply, Standard/Premium/Designer Sunmica, etc.
- **3 vendors**: Vendor A (timber), Vendor B (hardware), Vendor C (paints)
- **5 rate history records**, **3 inventory records**

---

## API Endpoints

| Method | Path | Role | Purpose |
|---|---|---|---|
| `GET` | `/api/materials/search?query=ply` | Any auth | Material picker search |
| `GET` | `/api/materials/{id}` | Any auth | Full material details |
| `POST` | `/api/quotations/create` | ADMIN | Create structured quotation |
| `GET` | `/api/quotations/{requestId}` | Any | Get quotation breakdown |
| `GET` | `/api/quotations/{requestId}/inventory-check` | ADMIN/SA | Check stock |
| `GET` | `/api/quotations/vendor-lists` | ADMIN/SA | Get vendor purchase lists |
| `PUT` | `/api/quotations/vendor-lists/{id}/mark-purchased` | ADMIN/SA | Mark item purchased |
| `POST` | `/api/request/{id}/approve-quotation` | REQUESTER | Approve quotation |
| `POST` | `/api/request/{id}/generate-vendor-list` | ADMIN/SA | Generate vendor list |

---

## Verification

**Backend**: `mvnw.cmd compile -q` → **Exit 0** (no errors) ✅

**To run E2E**:
1. Start DB → start backend (`mvnw.cmd spring-boot:run`)
2. DataInitializer seeds materials/vendors automatically
3. Start frontend (`npm run dev`)
4. Follow workflow: REQUESTER creates request → ADMIN reviews → ADMIN creates quotation (Materials page) → SA approves → REQUESTER approves quotation → ADMIN generates vendor list
